category: sans-serif
subsets: menu,latin

family: Xoxo

designer: Multiple Designers

approved: true
description: <p>Xoxo (Hugs and Kisses) is a very \
  low contrast sans serif font. It has very \
  short ascenders and a very high x hight. \
  Xoxo is a very playful font for long texts. \
  This font was originally designed to give \
  a cute and clean appearance to electronic \
  messages.</p> \
  <p>Designed by \
  <a href="https://plus.google.com/112934564034615336086/posts">NicolaÂ‡s \
  Silva (<a href="http://twitter.com/zar_nicolas20">@zar_nicolas20</a>) \
  and <a href="https://plus.google.com/104510930456899325757/posts">John \
  Vargas (<a href="http://twitter.com/vargas74">@vargas74</a>)</p>

font.Xoxo-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Xoxo-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

